  "body": "### Description\n\nhttps://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/actions/workflows/ci-kubernetes.yml should be extended to test integration surfaces of Quarkus with Kubernetes/OpenShift APIs. Namely the `quarkus-kubernetes-config` and `quarkus-kubernetes-service-binding` extensions come to mind.\r\n\r\nPurpose of this test coverage extension is to prevent introduction of regressions and to help with ensuring compatibility of with next releases of Kubernetes, and with that ensuring that workloads deployed and integrated with Kubernetes/OpenShift function properly.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
